{"article_id":"Rh3G3NxSl6Dve62N","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Twitter hid a tweet from President Trump early Friday","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"that the social media site said","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"broke its rules on \" glorifying violence , \"","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"then concealed the same tweet again","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"when it was later reposted from the official White House account .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The tweets in question directly threatened demonstrators after a chaotic third day of protests against the death of George Floyd in Minneapolis .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Demonstrators are demanding action over the death of the 46-year-old unarmed black man","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"after shocking video footage showed a white police officer","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"kneeling on his neck .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Late Thursday , they took over the Minneapolis Police Department 's third precinct","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and set the building ablaze .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Shortly after midnight , the president threatened to \" start shooting \" in an incendiary string of tweets .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Trump wrote :","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" These THUGS are dishonoring the memory of George Floyd ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and I won ' t let that happen .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Just spoke to Governor Tim Walz","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"and told him","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"that the Military is with him all the way .","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"Any difficulty","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"and we will assume control","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"but ,","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"when the looting starts ,","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"the shooting starts .","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"Thank you ! \"","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"The ' shooting ' reference echoed an infamous quote by an aggressive Miami police chief in 1967","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"who declared war on criminals","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"sowing unrest in black neighborhoods in Miami .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Now ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"instead of showing that tweet ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"the site displays a disclaimer","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that users have to click through","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"to be able to see what the president wrote .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"It states :","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"\" This Tweet violated the Twitter Rules","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"about glorifying violence .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"However , Twitter has determined","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that it may be in the public ' s interest for the Tweet to remain accessible . \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Predictably ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"when Trump woke up on Friday morning","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to find","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"his tweet has been hidden overnight ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"he and his allies went ballistic .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"The text of the concealed tweet was posted by the official White House account early Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"which was then slapped with the same warning .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"After the White House tweet was hidden ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"the official account responded :","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"\" This Tweet violated the Twitter Rules","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"about glorifying violence .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"However , Twitter has determined","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that it will allow terrorists , dictators , and foreign propagandists to abuse its platform. \"","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"The tweet included a screenshot from the feed of Iran ' s supreme leader , Ali Khamenei ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"calling for a violent jihad in Palestine .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"It ' s the first time","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"one of the president ' s tweets has been concealed by Twitter ,","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"and comes after a week","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"in which Trump has waged war on the site .","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"The president raged earlier this week","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"when Twitter added a fact-check to one of his tweets ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"casting doubt on his inaccurate assertion","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"that mail ballots would lead to widespread voting fraud .","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"Then , on Thursday , Trump signed an executive order","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"aimed at removing some legal protections","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"given to social media platforms .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"It urged federal regulators to crack down on companies like Twitter","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"and to consider removing legal protections","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"that exempt them from liability for what gets posted on their platforms .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"Reacting to the decision","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"to hide his tweet ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Trump frothed on Friday morning :","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"\" Twitter is doing nothing about all of the lies & propaganda","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"being put out by China or the Radical Left Democrat Party .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"They have targeted Republicans , Conservatives & the President of the United States . \"","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"He then claimed later on Friday","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"that he actually tweeted out of concern","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"that looting could lead to further violence ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"which could harm protesters .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"\" Looting leads to shooting ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"and that ' s why a man was shot and killed in Minneapolis on Wednesday night","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"- or look at what just happened in Louisville with 7 people shot .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"I don ' t want this to happen ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and that ' s what the expression","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"put out last night","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"means , \"","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"\" It was spoken as a fact , not as a statement . \"","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"Brendan Carr , commissioner of supposedly independent government agency the Federal Communications Commission , wrote :","depth":4},{"id":86,"text":"\" Twitter has abandoned any attempt at a good faith application of its rules .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"No one should take comfort in that .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"Here it is punishing speakers","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"based on whether it approves or disapproves of their politics . \"","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"White House Director of Social Media Dan Scavino added :","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"\" Twitter is targeting the President of the United States 24/7 ,","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"while turning their heads to protest organizers","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"who are planning , plotting , and communicating their next moves daily on this very platform .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Twitter is full of shit-more and more people are beginning to get it . \"","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":189,"left":160,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":150,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":121,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":105,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":99,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":0,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent